command:example.dev:code:
$BatchObjects = foreach ($request in $user) {
		New-JGraphBatchObject -Method GET -Url ('/users/' + $request + $QueryString)
	}
	Invoke-JGraphBatchRequest -BatchObjects $BatchObjects
Makes a new Batch-request

